1. *Promena* je neizbežna u životu. (Change is inevitable in life.)
2. Da li si primetio *promenu* u njenom ponašanju? (Have you noticed a change in her behavior?)
3. Njihov plan uključuje *promene* u poslovanju. (Their plan involves changes in business.)
4. Koliko puta si već napravio *promenu* frizure ove godine? (How many times have you changed your hairstyle this year?)
5. Neki ljudi se teško prilagođavaju na *promene* u okruženju. (Some people find it difficult to adapt to changes in their environment.)
6. Moramo napraviti *promenu* u našem pristupu ovom problemu. (We need to make a change in our approach to this problem.)
7. *Promena* se dešava postepeno i neprimetno. (Change happens gradually and imperceptibly.)
8. Nismo sigurni koliko će nova *promena* uticati na naš posao. (We're not sure how much the new change will affect our business.)
9. Naš tim će se suočiti sa mnogim *promenama* u narednom periodu. (Our team will face many changes in the coming period.)
10. Spreman sam da prihvatim *promenu* u svojoj karijeri. (I'm ready to accept a change in my career.)